msgid "Factory for modal dialogs on a world."
msgstr ""

#: miniworlds.worlds.dialog.DialogService:3 of
msgid ""
"All factory methods return immediately; the result is delivered to the "
"``callback`` (and stored in ``dialog.value`` after the dialog closed). "
"Cancelling a dialog (ESC) always delivers ``None``. Pass ``pause=True`` to "
"stop the world's logic (acting, timers, collisions) while the dialog is open."
msgstr ""

